1️⃣ VERBAL ABILITY – SYNONYMS, ANTONYMS & VOCABULARY

This section tests:

Word knowledge
Communication clarity
Reading skills
🔹 A. SYNONYMS (Same Meaning)
🔹 Example 1

Happy → Joyful

Fast → Quick

🔹 Example 2

Big → Large

Smart → Intelligent

🔹 B. ANTONYMS (Opposite Meaning)
🔹 Example 3

Hot → Cold

Easy → Difficult

🔹 Example 4

Success → Failure

Strong → Weak

🔹 C. COMMON PLACEMENT WORDS
Word	Meaning
Enhance	Improve
Rapid	Fast
Accurate	Correct
Decline	Decrease
Efficient	Productive
🔹 D. IMPORTANT TIP

👉 Don’t memorize blindly
👉 Understand meaning in context

🔹 Example 5

“Efficient worker”

Means → works quickly and correctly

